Class JetClientConfig

java.lang.Object
com.hazelcast.client.config.ClientConfig
com.hazelcast.jet.config.JetClientConfig
public class JetClientConfig
extends ClientConfig
A config object which is used for configuring the Jet client to connect to the Jet cluster.

See ClientConfig for actual config options.
